title: Dr Sampson Davis Phoner and more

description:
Today on the show we had a expert call up and give us more information about the Corona Virus and how to prevent others from getting it. Also, since it is Freak freaky Friday we opened up the phone lines to see what out listeners thought about certain things being essential, with one being dildos, after an Amazon worker spoke out about them not being as important. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Georgia Governor Brian Kemp for spreading misinformation.
